Dialogue: 2,0:00:00.17,0:00:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}This girl is Kouyama Mitsuki.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:02.31,0:00:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}She's twelve and dreams of becoming a singer.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:03.91,0:00:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}But unfortunately, she only has one year left to live.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:07.15,0:00:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Her manager has been selected
Dialogue: 2,0:00:08.48,0:00:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}and we went to Dr. Wakaouji's \Nplace to meet her, but...
Dialogue: 2,0:00:11.49,0:00:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}...we have to keep her secret\Nfrom being exposed. It's terrible!
Dialogue: 2,0:00:14.84,0:00:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}But hey, it's my job
Dialogue: 2,0:00:17.21,0:00:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}to get her through all these problems.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:20.28,0:00:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Well then...
Dialogue: 2,0:00:21.09,0:00:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}I wonder what's going to happen today.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:22.91,0:00:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:00:27.63,0:00:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,460)\be1}Do you understand?
Dialogue: 2,0:00:29.20,0:00:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,460)\be1}Yes.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:35.47,0:00:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Stop that at once, it's unladylike.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:37.93,0:00:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}How can you...
Dialogue: 2,0:00:39.23,0:00:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}...be so rude as to only worry about your skirt?
Dialogue: 2,0:00:42.81,0:00:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}You should be more attentive while eating.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:46.65,0:00:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}What is that sound?
Dialogue: 2,0:00:48.02,0:00:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}I-It's nothing!
Dialogue: 2,0:00:50.99,0:00:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}I'm sorry. I'll be more careful.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:52.96,0:00:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Good night.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:53.78,0:00:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Ah. Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:56.12,0:00:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}I haven't finished talking to...
Dialogue: 2,0:00:59.80,0:01:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Honestly, I really have to keep her on a short leash.
Dialogue: 2,0:01:04.51,0:01:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}That was close.
Dialogue: 2,0:01:07.84,0:01:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}H-Hello?
Dialogue: 2,0:01:09.61,0:01:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1\fscx85\fscy85}Ah. Mitsuki-chan? This is Ooshige.
