Dialogue: 2,0:01:13.16,0:01:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1\fscx85\fscy85}It's short notice, but
Dialogue: 2,0:01:14.19,0:01:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1\fscx85\fscy85}your debut single has been \Nselected to go on the market.
