Dialogue: 1,0:01:19.97,0:01:24.93,Episode Title,,0,0,0,Episode Title,{\pos(330,340)\bord2.5}The Feelings In Your Song
Dialogue: 2,0:01:29.51,0:01:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Mitsuki-chan.
Dialogue: 2,0:01:30.59,0:01:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}This is your producer, Takasu-sensei.
Dialogue: 2,0:01:33.94,0:01:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}I'm Kouyama Mitsuki.
Dialogue: 2,0:01:35.28,0:01:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}It's a pleasure to be working with you.
Dialogue: 2,0:01:36.58,0:01:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}The debut concept is...
Dialogue: 2,0:01:38.17,0:01:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}...the trouble of coming up with a cool and elite name.
Dialogue: 3,0:01:39.76,0:01:40.28,Overlap,,0,0,0,Dialogue (Overlap),{\pos(320,410)\be1}Eh?
Dialogue: 2,0:01:40.28,0:01:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Um... could you repeat that?
Dialogue: 2,0:01:43.09,0:01:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}If it's regarding that matter...
Dialogue: 2,0:01:44.56,0:01:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}...there is no question about my supporting you.
Dialogue: 2,0:01:46.81,0:01:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}I'm looking forward to working with you.
Dialogue: 2,0:01:48.80,0:01:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}What?
Dialogue: 2,0:01:49.61,0:01:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}There's no need for you to worry.
Dialogue: 2,0:01:51.28,0:01:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Together, we'll be sure to...
Dialogue: 2,0:01:52.94,0:01:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}...turn you into a sexy singer.
Dialogue: 2,0:01:56.28,0:01:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}S-Sexy you said?
Dialogue: 2,0:01:59.73,0:02:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}What... you're going to be late?
