Dialogue: 2,0:02:30.20,0:02:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}For now...
Dialogue: 2,0:02:31.29,0:02:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}...we're concentrating on your debut.
Dialogue: 2,0:02:33.79,0:02:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Um...
