Dialogue: 2,0:02:40.43,0:02:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}To say unsatisfied... well...
Dialogue: 2,0:02:43.01,0:02:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}This is...
Dialogue: 2,0:02:44.34,0:02:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}P-Please excuse us for a second!
