Dialogue: 2,0:02:52.45,0:02:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}You have to be more happy about it.
Dialogue: 2,0:02:54.61,0:02:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Takasu-san is...
Dialogue: 2,0:02:55.54,0:02:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}...the one who produced Matsushita Genki's and...
Dialogue: 2,0:02:57.28,0:02:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}...Kobayashi's debut.
Dialogue: 2,0:02:59.33,0:03:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}He's an amazing record producer.
