Dialogue: 2,0:03:21.93,0:03:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Why don't you try doing it... songwriting?
Dialogue: 2,0:03:27.44,0:03:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}I'm leaving this to you, Mitsuki-chan.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:30.90,0:03:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Man... these new artist nowadays are all so spoiled.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:33.87,0:03:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Well...
Dialogue: 2,0:03:34.61,0:03:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}...it's okay as long as you understand how futile it is.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:36.48,0:03:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}I'll try songwriting.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:38.32,0:03:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Eh?!
Dialogue: 2,0:03:39.62,0:03:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}It's just like you said.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:41.37,0:03:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}I'll try to put my feelings in it.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:43.60,0:03:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Thank you very much for the advice.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:45.97,0:03:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}That wasn't supposed to be advice...
Dialogue: 2,0:03:48.54,0:03:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}What? That's bad...
Dialogue: 2,0:03:51.23,0:03:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Got it. I'll be right there.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:54.04,0:03:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}It's fine. This'll be interesting.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:57.22,0:03:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}However, the time limit is three days.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:00.01,0:04:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Just how far can you go in three days.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:03.49,0:04:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}I want you to show me that.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:06.10,0:04:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}I... I'm very sorry!
Dialogue: 2,0:04:13.15,0:04:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Mitsuki-chan.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:14.64,0:04:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Yes?
Dialogue: 2,0:04:16.11,0:04:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}As your manager, there's something I want to ask you.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:19.53,0:04:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Y-Yes?
Dialogue: 2,0:04:20.60,0:04:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Who's Eichi-kun?
Dialogue: 2,0:04:22.47,0:04:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Tell me!
Dialogue: 2,0:04:27.20,0:04:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}I see...
Dialogue: 2,0:04:28.37,0:04:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}So you have someone you like.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:30.61,0:04:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Yes.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:31.79,0:04:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}But he left for America, and I\Nhaven't had any contact with him.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:35.87,0:04:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}My desire to become a singer is because...
Dialogue: 2,0:04:38.04,0:04:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}...if he heard me...
Dialogue: 2,0:04:39.71,0:04:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}...then maybe he'd notice me.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:41.60,0:04:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}That's what I think.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:44.18,0:04:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}All right!
Dialogue: 2,0:04:45.19,0:04:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:04:46.26,0:04:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}If that's the case, then I'll be rooting for you.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:48.80,0:04:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Really?
Dialogue: 2,0:04:50.01,0:04:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Yep.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:50.80,0:04:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}That song just now...
Dialogue: 2,0:04:51.89,0:04:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}...had no musical sense or good points to it at all.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:54.42,0:04:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}But... it'll be popular, right?
Dialogue: 2,0:04:57.06,0:04:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}You don't need to restrict yourself\Nto only song that will be popular.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:00.36,0:05:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}I want you... to debut with a good song.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:05.28,0:05:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Ooshige-san...
Dialogue: 2,0:05:07.07,0:05:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Write a good song...
Dialogue: 2,0:05:08.35,0:05:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}...and open Takasu-san's eyes!
Dialogue: 2,0:05:10.50,0:05:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Okay!
Dialogue: 2,0:05:18.00,0:05:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}All right...
Dialogue: 2,0:05:18.98,0:05:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}...let's start writing!
Dialogue: 2,0:05:25.26,0:05:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}What's wrong? Hurry up and write.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:27.66,0:05:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}I'd like to do that, but...
Dialogue: 2,0:05:29.46,0:05:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}I wonder how I'm supposed \Nto go about songwriting...
Dialogue: 2,0:05:32.48,0:05:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 2,0:05:33.27,0:05:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}...you don't know how to write songs!
Dialogue: 2,0:05:35.18,0:05:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Yeah...
Dialogue: 2,0:05:36.02,0:05:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Then why did you say you were going to write a song?!
Dialogue: 2,0:05:38.89,0:05:40.04,Overlap,,0,0,0,Dialogue (Overlap),{\pos(320,410)\be1}That's because...
Dialogue: 2,0:05:40.04,0:05:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}You have to be more upbeat when you're \Nsongwriting instead of suffering like you are now.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:43.80,0:05:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}What should I do?
Dialogue: 2,0:05:44.87,0:05:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}I have to finish it in three days...
Dialogue: 2,0:05:47.30,0:05:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Just leave it to me.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:50.49,0:05:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Do you have any CDs of a song anthology?
Dialogue: 2,0:05:53.24,0:05:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Yup. Just a sec.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:58.29,0:06:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Do you always keep it there?
Dialogue: 2,0:06:00.43,0:06:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Yup, it's easier for me to find them this way.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:03.93,0:06:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}See.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:06.38,0:06:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}That looks like it, but it's so worn out...
Dialogue: 2,0:06:09.94,0:06:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}This is the only thing I have that's music-related.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:14.16,0:06:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}I've read it over and over again.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:17.00,0:06:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}You're really so... valiant!
Dialogue: 2,0:06:21.04,0:06:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}By the way, Meroko...
Dialogue: 2,0:06:22.54,0:06:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}...what do you plan on doing about your song?
Dialogue: 2,0:06:25.44,0:06:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Well, that's...
Dialogue: 2,0:06:27.86,0:06:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Eh?
Dialogue: 2,0:06:29.96,0:06:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Meroko, what the hell are doing all of a sudden?!
Dialogue: 2,0:06:32.44,0:06:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}I can't understand what you're saying!
Dialogue: 2,0:06:37.00,0:06:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Anyways...
Dialogue: 2,0:06:38.47,0:06:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}...let go of my ha-...!
Dialogue: 2,0:06:42.13,0:06:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}What I just did was a hint.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:43.68,0:06:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Eh?
Dialogue: 2,0:06:44.50,0:06:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}So then, what was it?
Dialogue: 2,0:06:46.63,0:06:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}What the hell do you mean, "What is it?"
Dialogue: 2,0:06:48.16,0:06:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}All you did back there was clamp \Nyour big mouth over my hand!
Dialogue: 2,0:06:49.97,0:06:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Exactly.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:51.28,0:06:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}You should just shut your mouth.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:53.42,0:06:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}But... I wonder if I'll be okay doing something like that.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:56.24,0:06:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Of course not, there's no way you'll be okay!
Dialogue: 2,0:06:58.02,0:06:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}It'll be fine.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:59.60,0:07:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}You're doing this to see the\Nperson you like, after all.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:02.80,0:07:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}I guess so...
Dialogue: 2,0:07:05.33,0:07:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:07:06.33,0:07:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\fad(0,756)\be1}Do whatever you want!
Dialogue: 2,0:07:15.03,0:07:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}W-What was that for?
Dialogue: 2,0:07:18.29,0:07:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Now Takuto will be all lovey-dovey with me.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:23.38,0:07:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Man...
Dialogue: 2,0:07:24.25,0:07:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}You said to leave the songwriting to you...
Dialogue: 2,0:07:26.72,0:07:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}and you're already sick of it.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:28.18,0:07:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:07:31.22,0:07:32.46,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}She's...
Dialogue: 2,0:07:52.95,0:07:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}I guess it can't be helped.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:11.95,0:08:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}You're up early.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:13.08,0:08:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Ah, Takuto.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:15.10,0:08:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Good morning.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:18.81,0:08:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}By the way, are you okay in just your pajamas?
Dialogue: 2,0:08:22.19,0:08:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Yeah. I seem fine.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:23.99,0:08:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}I guess I forgot about my sickness.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:26.34,0:08:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Forgot...?
Dialogue: 2,0:08:27.91,0:08:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}It's the first time I've ever\Nforgotten about my sickness.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:32.95,0:08:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Doing what I want to, with all my heart...
Dialogue: 2,0:08:35.21,0:08:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}...it feels so good.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:38.20,0:08:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}And... it was you, right?
Dialogue: 2,0:08:40.01,0:08:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:08:41.08,0:08:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}This.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:43.38,0:08:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}That's why I'm fine.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:46.04,0:08:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Thank you!
Dialogue: 2,0:08:49.14,0:08:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}A-Anyways, did you finish writing?
Dialogue: 2,0:08:51.55,0:08:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Yeah. I finished writing, but...
Dialogue: 2,0:08:55.36,0:08:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}What is it?
Dialogue: 2,0:08:57.05,0:08:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Meroko.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:57.97,0:08:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Let's see.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:01.60,0:09:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}H-How is it?
Dialogue: 2,0:09:04.09,0:09:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Well...
Dialogue: 2,0:09:05.06,0:09:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}How should I put it...
Dialogue: 2,0:09:07.50,0:09:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Huh? If you don't get it, then let me have a look at it.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:10.52,0:09:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1\i1}If you're smiling... it's like a clear day.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:13.99,0:09:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1\i1}If you're crying... it's like a great flood.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:16.20,0:09:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1\i1}As long as I am by your side,\Nit'll always be smiles and peace.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:19.60,0:09:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}What's this suppose to be?
Dialogue: 2,0:09:20.84,0:09:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}As I thought... they're no good, huh.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:22.62,0:09:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}I-I wouldn't say that they're no good...
Dialogue: 2,0:09:24.70,0:09:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:25.16,0:09:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}The first time's probably like this.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:27.04,0:09:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}It's okay.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:27.92,0:09:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}I know that I can't do it by myself.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:30.67,0:09:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}I've never done it before, after all.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:33.21,0:09:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}There isn't time to learn.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:35.15,0:09:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Why don't you go on a date once, then?
Dialogue: 2,0:09:37.76,0:09:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Eh?!
Dialogue: 2,0:09:38.72,0:09:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Sure.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:39.44,0:09:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}If you do that, you'll be able to write something.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:41.11,0:09:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}But... how?
Dialogue: 2,0:09:42.81,0:09:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}There's no one to go with.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:44.50,0:09:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}T-That's right...
Dialogue: 2,0:09:47.27,0:09:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}I thought it was a good idea...
Dialogue: 2,0:09:53.57,0:09:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Good morning, Mitsuki-chan!
Dialogue: 2,0:09:55.44,0:09:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}How are you feeling this morning?
Dialogue: 2,0:09:58.61,0:10:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}There he is!
Dialogue: 2,0:10:00.12,0:10:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}The person who you're going on a date with!
Dialogue: 2,0:10:01.92,0:10:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Eh?!
Dialogue: 2,0:10:02.64,0:10:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}A date with Wakaouji-sensei?!
Dialogue: 2,0:10:19.33,0:10:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Wow!
Dialogue: 2,0:10:21.43,0:10:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}This is the first time I've ever been to Harajuku!
Dialogue: 2,0:10:25.56,0:10:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}You're this happy about coming here... I'm glad.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:29.19,0:10:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}I was really surprised when you\Nasked me on a date, though.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:34.27,0:10:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Well, as long as you're this\Nhappy, your body will get better.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:37.27,0:10:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Okay!
Dialogue: 2,0:10:38.11,0:10:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}All right!
Dialogue: 2,0:10:38.88,0:10:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Let's start our date.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:40.82,0:10:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Okay!
Dialogue: 2,0:10:54.38,0:10:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Wow!
Dialogue: 2,0:10:55.53,0:10:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}This is really good!
Dialogue: 2,0:10:56.81,0:10:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Isn't it?
Dialogue: 2,0:10:57.78,0:11:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}I was sure that you would like it.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:01.84,0:11:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Just what you would expect from a little girl's escort.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:04.88,0:11:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Heh. He's not doing much.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:06.73,0:11:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}So... how's the date?
Dialogue: 2,0:11:09.00,0:11:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}This is more fun than your job, right?
Dialogue: 2,0:11:11.02,0:11:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Yep!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:11.70,0:11:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}I had lots of fun!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:13.77,0:11:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}It's almost as if I was on a date with Eichi-kun.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:17.17,0:11:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Ah!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:20.15,0:11:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Sometimes when you're staring at the sky...
Dialogue: 2,0:11:22.29,0:11:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}...you're thinking about Eichi-kun, aren't you?
Dialogue: 2,0:11:25.49,0:11:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Eichi-kun, Eichi-kun...
Dialogue: 2,0:11:28.37,0:11:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}She's so cute!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:29.71,0:11:30.46,Overlap,,0,0,0,Dialogue (Overlap),{\pos(320,410)\be1}Not really...
Dialogue: 2,0:11:31.05,0:11:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Well...
Dialogue: 2,0:11:32.30,0:11:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}...it's about time.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:33.96,0:11:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Shall we head back?
Dialogue: 2,0:11:35.29,0:11:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Okay!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:39.82,0:11:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Mitsuki-chan!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:41.41,0:11:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Are you all right?
Dialogue: 2,0:11:42.76,0:11:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Mitsuki-chan!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:43.87,0:11:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Yes.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:44.66,0:11:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}I'm fine.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:47.65,0:11:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Mitsuki-chan!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:49.37,0:11:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Mitsuki-chan, hold on!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:52.42,0:11:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Mitsuki-chan!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:59.20,0:12:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}The medicine's taken effect, right?
Dialogue: 2,0:12:01.29,0:12:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Your fever's gone down,
Dialogue: 2,0:12:02.74,0:12:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}and you don't seem like coughing anymore.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:04.48,0:12:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:05.68,0:12:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}It's because I was thinking selfishly.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:07.50,0:12:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}No.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:08.66,0:12:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}It was my fault for being careless.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:10.83,0:12:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}That's not it.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:12.15,0:12:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Last night... I stayed up.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:14.40,0:12:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}You stayed up?
Dialogue: 2,0:12:15.64,0:12:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}It couldn't have been because of your job.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:20.48,0:12:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}I certainly agreed to your working, but...
Dialogue: 2,0:12:23.15,0:12:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}...if you do such unreasonable things,
Dialogue: 2,0:12:25.22,0:12:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}I can't allow you to continue being a model.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:29.63,0:12:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Sensei! Please stop saying that!
Dialogue: 2,0:12:32.51,0:12:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}I want to debut no matter what!
Dialogue: 2,0:12:34.71,0:12:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}If I don't debut...
Dialogue: 2,0:12:35.77,0:12:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}...I won't be able to let Eichi-kun know that I'm here.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:39.20,0:12:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}I... I...
Dialogue: 2,0:12:43.27,0:12:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}I understand.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:45.44,0:12:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}You don't need to say any more.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:47.04,0:12:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}If I oppose you, I'll just be the bad guy.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:50.00,0:12:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Don't worry.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:51.28,0:12:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}I'll still back you up.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:53.14,0:12:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Really?!
Dialogue: 2,0:12:54.85,0:12:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Of course.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:55.87,0:12:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}But don't do anything unreasonable from now on.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:58.36,0:12:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Okay!
Dialogue: 2,0:12:59.23,0:13:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Eichi again, huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:13:00.90,0:13:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}To be thought about this much... Eichi must be happy.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:04.56,0:13:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}I also won't do anything like... giving up on Takuto!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:07.34,0:13:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Let me go already!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:09.97,0:13:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}I'll excuse myself, then.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:20.23,0:13:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 2,0:13:21.56,0:13:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}The medicine's working, so I'll...
Dialogue: 2,0:13:24.08,0:13:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Stop it.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:25.21,0:13:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Go to sleep.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:26.44,0:13:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}I can't fall asleep.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:28.63,0:13:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}There's only one day left to write a song.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:32.25,0:13:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Hey, Takuto.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:33.75,0:13:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Can you turn me into a sixteen year old again?
Dialogue: 2,0:13:35.65,0:13:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Then you won't have to worry about my health, right?
Dialogue: 2,0:13:38.73,0:13:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}That's true, but...
Dialogue: 2,0:13:40.92,0:13:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Why do you have to do such unreasonable things?!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:43.63,0:13:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Isn't it fine?!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:45.34,0:13:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}That producer Takasu's songs...
Dialogue: 2,0:13:47.76,0:13:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}...they'll be a hit, right?
Dialogue: 2,0:13:49.95,0:13:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}I don't want a song that's just a hit.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:52.86,0:13:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}I have to send my feelings to Eichi-kun properly.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:59.36,0:14:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Just stop it already.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:00.67,0:14:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:14:01.53,0:14:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Takuto?
Dialogue: 2,0:14:03.01,0:14:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Stop trying to write songs like that!
Dialogue: 2,0:14:05.36,0:14:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 2,0:14:07.19,0:14:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Just give up already.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:08.70,0:14:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Besides, writing a song is impossible for you.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:12.88,0:14:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}W-Wait... Hold up,
Dialogue: 2,0:14:14.92,0:14:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Takuto!
Dialogue: 2,0:14:16.15,0:14:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Takuto!
Dialogue: 2,0:14:17.50,0:14:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Takuto!
Dialogue: 2,0:14:22.96,0:14:24.76,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}My voice won't come out.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:24.76,0:14:27.76,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}If Takuto isn't here, I...
Dialogue: 2,0:14:30.03,0:14:32.95,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}...won't ever again... like that...
Dialogue: 2,0:14:34.10,0:14:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}What should I do?
Dialogue: 2,0:14:40.56,0:14:42.17,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Man.. what's with her?
Dialogue: 2,0:14:42.61,0:14:46.19,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\fad(210,0)\be1}Everything she says is Eichi, Eichi, Eichi.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:46.48,0:14:48.42,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}It's so annoying!
Dialogue: 2,0:14:51.11,0:14:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Takuto, wait up!
Dialogue: 2,0:14:53.87,0:14:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Wait up, I said!
Dialogue: 2,0:14:55.63,0:14:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}What's wrong with you, saying something like that...
Dialogue: 2,0:14:58.23,0:14:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:15:02.33,0:15:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}What's with you... stopping so suddenly...
Dialogue: 2,0:15:04.72,0:15:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Meroko.
Dialogue: 2,0:15:05.48,0:15:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:15:09.88,0:15:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}It kinda looks like they're arguing.
Dialogue: 2,0:15:13.06,0:15:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Let's check it out.
Dialogue: 2,0:15:14.86,0:15:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Okay.
Dialogue: 2,0:15:17.31,0:15:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}What is the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 2,0:15:18.72,0:15:19.33,Sync,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1\i1}Huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 2,0:15:19.61,0:15:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}What's "the song is already done" supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 2,0:15:22.35,0:15:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Just what I said.
Dialogue: 2,0:15:24.43,0:15:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}The songs have been altered.
Dialogue: 2,0:15:26.82,0:15:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}That can't be.
Dialogue: 2,0:15:28.03,0:15:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Back there you promised Mitsuki-chan\Nshe could write her own so-...!
Dialogue: 2,0:15:30.66,0:15:32.60,Overlap,,0,0,0,Dialogue (Overlap),{\pos(320,380)\be1}If this project fails...
Dialogue: 2,0:15:32.60,0:15:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}...do you understand how much will be lost?
Dialogue: 2,0:15:35.40,0:15:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Leaving it to an amateur...
Dialogue: 2,0:15:36.84,0:15:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}...did you really think that I'd do that?
Dialogue: 2,0:15:39.92,0:15:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}T-That's...
Dialogue: 2,0:15:41.42,0:15:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}But, a promise is a promise!
Dialogue: 2,0:15:44.38,0:15:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}How naive.
Dialogue: 2,0:15:45.52,0:15:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}You can't think like that in this world.
Dialogue: 2,0:15:50.33,0:15:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Ow! Ow!
Dialogue: 2,0:15:51.68,0:15:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Ow!
Dialogue: 2,0:15:54.07,0:15:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Good job, you.
Dialogue: 2,0:15:55.32,0:15:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Open your eyes.
Dialogue: 2,0:15:56.46,0:15:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}There's no way someone like you could\Never understand Mitsuki's feelings.
Dialogue: 2,0:15:59.28,0:16:00.65,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}That's right.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:00.69,0:16:03.34,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}She... always remembers her\Npromises, no matter who they're with.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:06.61,0:16:08.20,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Even thought I knew that...
Dialogue: 2,0:16:08.61,0:16:11.34,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}I... what did I do..?!
Dialogue: 2,0:16:11.49,0:16:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}I'm going back.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:13.10,0:16:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Wait!
Dialogue: 2,0:16:13.98,0:16:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Geez... what's with you?
Dialogue: 3,0:16:12.08,0:16:13.97,Overlap,,0,0,0,Dialogue (Overlap),{\pos(320,410)\be1\fscy85\fscx85}What are you doing to my head?!
Dialogue: 3,0:16:14.45,0:16:15.97,Overlap,,0,0,0,Dialogue (Overlap),{\pos(320,410)\be1\fscy85\fscx85}This is very sensitive!
Dialogue: 2,0:16:15.97,0:16:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1\fscy85\fscx85}Ow! That place hurts!
Dialogue: 2,0:16:17.59,0:16:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1\fscy85\fscx85}Ow!
Dialogue: 2,0:16:26.00,0:16:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Mitsuki...
Dialogue: 2,0:16:27.60,0:16:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Back there, I...
Dialogue: 2,0:16:29.56,0:16:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 2,0:16:31.28,0:16:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Hurry up and stop that.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:37.21,0:16:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Back there, I...
Dialogue: 2,0:16:38.52,0:16:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Takuto...?
Dialogue: 2,0:16:39.47,0:16:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:16:41.24,0:16:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Then... this is...
Dialogue: 2,0:16:43.12,0:16:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}While I was writing my song...
Dialogue: 2,0:16:44.69,0:16:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}...Grandma kept coming in and checking on me.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:47.59,0:16:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}So I pretended that I was under my blanket.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:50.88,0:16:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Wh-What in the..?!
Dialogue: 2,0:16:52.42,0:16:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Takuto.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:53.58,0:16:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}I'm sorry about earlier.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:55.39,0:16:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}E-Er... that's supposed to be my line.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:57.92,0:17:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}I've been only depending on you guys for everything.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:02.45,0:17:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Wanting to debut... and wanting to see Eichi-kun...
Dialogue: 2,0:17:05.45,0:17:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}...those are all part of my dream.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:07.42,0:17:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}If I don't work hard myself...
Dialogue: 2,0:17:09.52,0:17:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}...that'd be wrong, right?
Dialogue: 2,0:17:13.77,0:17:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}You've been writing the whole time since then?
Dialogue: 2,0:17:16.13,0:17:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Yeah.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:17.03,0:17:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}I've thrown away a lot of drafts.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:20.14,0:17:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}But it was fun to think this much about a song.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:23.86,0:17:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Eh?
Dialogue: 2,0:17:25.10,0:17:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}I really do love singing!
Dialogue: 2,0:17:29.73,0:17:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Earlier, when I thought about \Nnever being able to sing again...
Dialogue: 2,0:17:32.67,0:17:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}...I was really sad.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:34.28,0:17:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}It was painful...
Dialogue: 2,0:17:36.45,0:17:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}I want to see Eichi-kun, of course, but...
Dialogue: 2,0:17:39.70,0:17:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}...I want to sing just as much!
Dialogue: 2,0:17:43.24,0:17:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}This feeling makes my heart skip!
Dialogue: 2,0:17:45.96,0:17:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}I can't make it stop!
Dialogue: 2,0:17:49.33,0:17:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}That's it.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:50.42,0:17:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Eh? That's it?
Dialogue: 2,0:17:52.92,0:17:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Use the true words that came from your heart...
Dialogue: 2,0:17:55.59,0:17:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}...try singing with those.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:58.31,0:18:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Put these feelings into my song?
Dialogue: 2,0:18:00.76,0:18:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Yeah.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:01.44,0:18:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}But...
Dialogue: 2,0:18:02.08,0:18:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}I wonder if I can say it well.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:03.60,0:18:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}You told me just fine.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:07.52,0:18:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Me, too.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:10.39,0:18:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Okay!
Dialogue: 2,0:18:11.18,0:18:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}I got it! I'll try it!
Dialogue: 2,0:18:13.46,0:18:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}That's it.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:14.36,0:18:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}That's the spirit!
Dialogue: 2,0:18:15.97,0:18:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Work hard!
Dialogue: 2,0:18:17.60,0:18:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Okay!
Dialogue: 2,0:18:24.53,0:18:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}This is the best I can do towards expressing my feelings.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:27.14,0:18:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Please take a look at them.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:28.96,0:18:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Well. I'll at least take a look at it.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:40.80,0:18:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Well, it can't be helped.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:45.35,0:18:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}This is Takasu.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:46.93,0:18:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}For Kouyama Mitsuki's song, \NI've selected a different one.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:50.59,0:18:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:18:51.34,0:18:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}That means...
Dialogue: 2,0:18:52.47,0:18:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}I lost.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:53.64,0:18:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Writing with such will...
Dialogue: 2,0:18:55.72,0:18:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}...the concept and the feeling... it's all there.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:58.25,0:18:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}That means...
Dialogue: 2,0:18:59.67,0:19:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}You did it!
Dialogue: 2,0:19:00.76,0:19:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}It's been accepted!
Dialogue: 2,0:19:01.66,0:19:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Your song's been chosen!
Dialogue: 2,0:19:03.41,0:19:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Eh? Really?!
Dialogue: 2,0:19:05.59,0:19:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Yes, even though you have a tight schedule.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:08.00,0:19:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}It's all due to your rash actions.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:09.80,0:19:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Prepare yourself.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:11.44,0:19:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}It's going to be busy.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:12.96,0:19:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Yes! We'll do our best!
Dialogue: 2,0:19:15.02,0:19:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}By the way...
Dialogue: 2,0:19:15.90,0:19:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}...what are you going to use for a stage name?
Dialogue: 2,0:19:17.37,0:19:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:19:18.03,0:19:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}That's right...
Dialogue: 2,0:19:19.21,0:19:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}What should we use?
Dialogue: 2,0:19:20.02,0:19:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Do you want to just go with your real name?
Dialogue: 2,0:19:21.35,0:19:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}N-No, that'll be bad...
Dialogue: 2,0:19:23.52,0:19:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Um...
Dialogue: 2,0:19:27.14,0:19:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1\i1}Hey, Mitsuki.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:29.68,0:19:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1\i1}If by chance the two of us are separated...
Dialogue: 2,0:19:32.74,0:19:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1\i1}...there's no need to worry.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:34.54,0:19:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1\i1}Why?
Dialogue: 2,0:19:36.50,0:19:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1\i1}Even if we're at the ends of the world...
Dialogue: 2,0:19:38.66,0:19:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1\i1}...the moon will be in the sky.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:40.98,0:19:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1\i1}So, I'll look in the sky for the moon...
Dialogue: 2,0:19:44.72,0:19:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1\i1}That's why you have to shine even brighter...
Dialogue: 2,0:19:47.98,0:19:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\fad(0,200)\be1\i1}...so that I can find you sooner.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:56.62,0:19:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}I've decided.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:59.35,0:20:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}I've chosen Full Moon.
Dialogue: 2,0:21:35.34,0:21:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Yo-re-i-ho!
Dialogue: 2,0:21:36.96,0:21:38.26,Overlap,,0,0,0,Dialogue (Overlap),{\pos(320,410)\be1}What was that all of a sudden?!
Dialogue: 2,0:21:38.26,0:21:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}That's because... look, look...
Dialogue: 2,0:21:39.58,0:21:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}...at this setting.
Dialogue: 2,0:21:40.42,0:21:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}A blue sky. Green mountains.
Dialogue: 2,0:21:42.44,0:21:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}The air is so fresh...
Dialogue: 2,0:21:44.24,0:21:45.76,Overlap,,0,0,0,Dialogue (Overlap),{\pos(320,410)\be1}We didn't come to play around!
Dialogue: 2,0:21:45.78,0:21:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}This is her first job, after all.
Dialogue: 2,0:21:47.76,0:21:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}We have to keep an eye on her.
Dialogue: 2,0:21:49.18,0:21:50.49,Overlap,,0,0,0,Dialogue (Overlap),{\pos(320,410)\be1}I get it.
Dialogue: 2,0:21:50.49,0:21:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}But I wonder if that girl can pull it off.
Dialogue: 2,0:21:53.24,0:21:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}When you say that...
Dialogue: 2,0:21:54.37,0:21:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Inside, she's still a twelve year old...
Dialogue: 2,0:21:57.08,0:21:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Next time on Full Moon wo Sagashite:
Dialogue: 2,0:21:59.25,0:22:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}The First Job.
